name: Password Cracker
description:
Password Cracker is game where player have to guess 4 different digits.

In Single Attack mode player have unlimited time and unlimited moves to crack the password.

In Time Attack mode player have 45 seconds and unlimited moves to crack the password.

In Restricted Attack player have 8 attempts and unlimited time to crack the password.

.NET 3.0 Required, NOT included.
